{"tid":156334,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解總係有啲戇鳩仔鍾意講「我朋友重勁呀！...」？","createTime":"2017-03-14T15:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T04:46:02.000Z","uid":5866,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cfb6e11cd9d4a597882092e6f7928bacf89bcfc","tid":156334,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:55:55.000Z","msg":"有冇試過遇過𠵱啲人？當人哋享緊一啲自身嘅經歷嘅時候，某條友總係咁啱有「朋友」經歷過相同嘅情況，而且結局一定係比其他人嘅更「勁」<br />\n<br />\n係呀，你「朋友」好撚勁呀<br />\n人哋話自己試過2日唔瞓，你就話你個「朋友」重勁試過一個禮拜唔瞓呀<br />\n人哋話自己操咗肌肉三個月開始有少少成效，你就話你個「朋友」重勁操咗三個月就肌肉爆棚<br />\n人哋話自己打機中咗一啲好撚稀有嘅寶物，你就話你個「朋友」重勁呀，前個幾日連中幾次添呀<br />\n但個寶物明明出咗唔夠一日<br />\n<br />\n根本𠵱啲戇鳩仔就係唔抵得自己廢過人，見人經歷有趣/覺得好勁就眼紅，死唔甘心噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自己又駁唔到，於是就不斷作個「朋友」出嚟，為求平衡下自己，自我感覺良好，等自己冇噉柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好心啦，就算真係有個位「朋友」呀，噉都係個「朋友」勁啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到好似關自己事噉，唔好噉樣衰啦，你係威嘅，就用自己嚟講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ce9ea4c9234447464ab2e6503162aef2d3a5e4","tid":156334,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:59:04.000Z","msg":"我朋友既程度仲勁過你朋友"},{"pid":"447e1f078433b87cec81c4f06beb68dcfbeaed5c","tid":156334,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我朋友既程度仲勁過你朋友</blockquote><br />\n我朋友仲勁過俾你朋友勁過果個朋友"},{"pid":"a5a6ad44e665d6fd065a68d9bab3c2e595a9c8f6","tid":156334,"uid":66213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"操肌個到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起之前都係啱啱開始操，同另一個fd傾緊點操個時有條友話：「你地都操緊呀？搵日得閒跟下我去做啦，等我D fd蝦下你地，你地推幾多呀？我個fd推XX KG呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n問佢推咩佢連個動作名都講唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋佢小肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389426ed4da2ad64a2274ef85044ab8a6c77664e","tid":156334,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"台灣不嬲都有<br />\n<br />\n呢個term叫 強者我朋友😂"},{"pid":"47414d7a101283d9778b6f4e936e9244ffa14b70","tid":156334,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:40:39.000Z","msg":"我朋友重戇鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39128e0156c38f9d7b7000efbcfa4208b65587f","tid":156334,"uid":22116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我朋友重戇鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有冇答佢物以類聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb7e74aa5b89b6014aa4c10ae76cd77e6870004","tid":156334,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"我朋友仲勁呀 佢勁到冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}